snippet.title: Farrah Abraham Returns To Reunite With Maci Bookout & Amber Portwood on ‘Teen Mom: Family Reunion’
snippet.description:
MTV Teen Mom OG’s Amber Portwood storms off of ‘Teen Mom: OG’ Reunion special after her ex-Gary Shirley shared their daughter Leah’s therapy revelation.

Farrah Abraham making a STUNNING return to the ‘Teen Mom’ franchise… and so much more on your favorite ‘Teen Mom’ stars!

We’ve got all this covered and more in this week’s edition of 'InTouch With Teen Mom.'
